    "text": "embeddings into the $D \\times N$ matrix $\\mathbf{H}_{k}$ and post-multiply by the adjacency matrix $\\mathbf{A}$, the $n^{th}$ column of the result is $\\text{agg}[n, k]$. The update for the nodes is now:"
